fields.titulo: Lewis Hamilton wins the Australian Grand Prix
fields.corpo: Lewis Hamilton dominated the Australian Grand Prix, taking the victory by over 20 seconds. It was a dominant performance from the Mercedes driver, who led every lap of the race from pole position. Max Verstappen finished second for Red Bull, with Valtteri Bottas taking third place for Mercedes.

fields.titulo: Max Verstappen wins the Bahrain Grand Prix
fields.corpo: Max Verstappen took a surprise victory at the Bahrain Grand Prix, taking the lead on the final lap after a strategic gamble by Red Bull paid off. Lewis Hamilton finished second for Mercedes, with Valtteri Bottas taking third place. It was a dramatic race, with multiple lead changes and several incidents on track.

fields.titulo: Max Verstappen wins the Azerbaijan Grand Prix
fields.corpo: Max Verstappen took a dramatic victory at the Azerbaijan Grand Prix, taking the lead on the final lap after a strategic gamble by Red Bull paid off. Lewis Hamilton finished second for Mercedes, with Valtteri Bottas taking third place. It was a chaotic race, with multiple lead changes and several incidents on track.

fields.titulo: Lewis Hamilton wins the Spanish Grand Prix
fields.corpo: Lewis Hamilton took his third victory of the season at the Spanish Grand Prix, dominating the race from start to finish. Max Verstappen finished second for Red Bull, with Valtteri Bottas taking third place for Mercedes. It was a relatively uneventful race, with few on-track incidents and few changes in the running order.
